Package main

Class Team

java.lang.Object
main.Team
public class Team extends Object
Represents a team that consists of Athletes. The athletes are stored in a list that is also divided into smaller subsections, referred to as 'subteams', which are used to group athletes into positions. The Attackers subteam consists of the Attacker positions, the Defender subteam consists of the defender positions, and so on. Reserves are also treated as a subteam, though do not actively participate in Matches The size of the team, and hence size of the subteams (excluding reserves which is always 5), is determined at the start of the game.
Version:
1.12
Author:
mdi48, bsm62
